description:
&lt;p&gt;The Trust is seeking to recruit an IT Desktop Technician to primarily provide support to users of IT systems and services at Harrogate Hospital and secondarily to provide support to users at our community sites in North Yorkshire. You will support the use of hardware, software and telecommunications in the organisation, including providing high level onsite and remote IT technical liaison, support and network administration to computer users across the full lifecycle of incidents and problems. You will also receive and resolve requests for support and providing where appropriate, some technical fault diagnosis, advice and guidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role involves close working with all teams within the IT function and throughout the wider organisation, ensuring a quality client-focused service is delivered to users and providing first line support to users of IT systems and services across the organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stuart Wilson - IT Team Leader&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;stuart.wilson8@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
